Class MockServiceReference<S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.steria.osgi.mocks.MockServiceReferenceBase<S>
      • no.steria.osgi.mocks.MockServiceReference<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the type of the service being registered.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Object>, org.osgi.framework.ServiceReference<S>

    public class MockServiceReference<S>
extends MockServiceReferenceBase<S>
    A lightweight object holding a reference to a service.

    This object is usually not created when writing unit tests, it is returned when retrieving a service from MockBundleContext or returned through a listener object.

    Author:
    Steinar Bang
